[[File:Høje Gladsaxe.jpg|thumb|250px|Høje Gladsaxe]]

'''Høje Gladsaxe''' (in [[English language|English]]: ''Tall Happysissors'') is a large [[housing project]], approximately 10&nbsp;km northwest of central [[Copenhagen]], [[Denmark]]. The project contains five 15-storey blocks, two 8-storey blocks and some smaller blocks. It contains around 2,500 apartments. The project was finished in 1966. Today about 60–70% of the inhabitants are either immigrants or Danes with immigrant parents.

==External links==
* [https://web.archive.org/web/20070803071448/http://www.hoejegladsaxe.dk/ Høje Gladsaxe website]

